## ‚úçÔ∏è Typesetting Rules

### Padding & Bounding
- Text sits inside a bounding box based on `line-height`
- Use **even vertical padding** inside the box (e.g. `center` alignment)
- Use **fixed spacing values** from edge to text container:
  ```
  Label ‚Üí 16px
  Title ‚Üí 16px
  Body ‚Üí 20px (line height)
  ```

### Baseline Method
- Android/text-native layouts rely on **baseline spacing**
- Measure from the baseline of one text element to another
- Good for typographic precision across platforms

